  <brief_title>Special Drug Use Investigation for ADOAIR DISKUS COPD (Salmeterol and Fluticasone)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Special Drug Use Investigation for ADOAIR DISKUS COPD (Salmeterol and Fluticasone)</official_title>
